# group_action_ontology
##the simplest consensus mechanism:

###input

<i> will join <cause> if <amount of people> join

###pseudocode

check(declaration_of_willingness_to_join):
	d = declaration_of_willingness_to_join
	c = d.cause
	count = 0
	for p in Persons:
		if p.has_declaration_of_willingness d2 and d2.has_cause c and d2.limit <= d.limit:
			count += 1
	if count >= d.limit:
		alert the user



